Package rs.ac.ns.ftn.tmd.datatypes

Interface Summary
FuzzySet A class which defines operations Fuzzy Numbers have to support, independantly to its inner implementation.
 

Class Summary
CrispSet Esta clase es la implementacion de un conjunto numerico y hereda directamente de la clase FuzzySet.
DecomposedFuzzyNumber Implementation of decomposed fuzzy numbers and fuzzy arithmetics between them
FuzzyFactory  
FuzzyInterval Esta clase implementa un intervalo borroso.
LRFuzzyNumber Implementation of L-R fuzzy numbers and arithmetics between them
ScalarNumber Esta clase implementa un valor escalar simple.
